Description:
The ORR needs a clear understanding that digital signalling proposals are being managed appropriately and can be supported in the Periodic Review1 process.

We require a specialist team to assess and report on Network Rail's signalling renewals plan with a particular focus on:
-Long-Term Deployment Plan (LTDP)
-Target 190plus research and development programme.

The specialist team will provide advice to us on the following areas:
•Decision making processes within Network Rail on the signalling renewals programme;
•signalling renewals projects planned in CP7 and the associated risks and opportunities;
•interfaces between conventional-partial signalling renewals, digital-ready renewals and digital renewals;
•commitments in the LTDP for CP7 and beyond and the critical path for delivery; and
•how Network Rail has evidenced benefits through its T190plus research and development programme.

The existing insulation and roof covering will be stripped back to the existing deck and a new Bauder Total Roof System installed.
•	Upgrade the Thermal performance of the existing roofs;
•	Install new Flat Roof Bauder System to provide a 20yr insurance backed warranty;
•	Upgrade the roof drainage;
•	Provide new Fascia boards as required;
•	Existing Roof lights to be changed to Triple Skin Rooflights.

